\cf0 1. Add a part to the vignette. (It doesn't matter what part. Just pick one.) \
2. Open the inspector (Tools
\f4 \'ae
\f2 Show Info).\
3. Select the part name field (it'll be something like "3001.dat") and change it to read "Joe Vig"\'d1the submodel name\'d1instead. Hit return.\
4. You should now see Joe in the vignette. Joe will now be treated as a single piece that can be move in one big chunk. It'll be much easier to stuff Joe down the well to make "Disaster at the Well" complete now!\
